description: Pollo " A Gourmet Chicken Joint", is Louisville, Kentucky's first street food vendor devoted to making great chicken meals. The combination of taking gourmet fast food makes for a fun experience with a unique ambiance. The Pollo Bus and Pollo Cart are definitely not your traditional food stand, cooking up the best you will ever have when it comes to fried chicken or chicken and waffles.Treat your taste buds to a number one place!
name: POLLO "A Gourmet Chicken Joint"
